snippet.textDisplay:
The amazing music to come out of Coke Studio in both Pakistan and India is incredible. I love that there have been cross-border collaborations, including this lovely track with Shilpa Rao, one of my favorite singers, contributing in such a grand way. 

I wish I understood the lyrics a lot better -- the dialect they're using definitely goes over my head. Regardless, though, one of my favorite tracks of Season 9!
